== 事件 ==
1973年11月27日，公園發生女屍案，17歲工廠女工陳月娟晚飯後在家收到男性朋友電話後外出，整晚沒有回家。到28日清晨，九龍仔公園清潔工發現延文禮士道正門圍牆下有一名滿身傷痕的女子屍體，驗屍後證實女子被毒打致死，之後棄屍九龍仔公園正門圍牆，陳月娟家人於29日報案時確認死者身份，1974年3月警方懸紅15000元緝兇，目前仍未破案。<ref>{{cite news|title=九龍仔公園前艷屍 死者身世迄未明|url=https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=%28%20%28%20allTermsMandatory%3A%28true%29%20OR+all_dc.title%3A%28%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%29%20OR+all_dc.creator%3A%28%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%29%20OR+all_dc.contributor%3A%28%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%29%20OR+all_dc.subject%3A%28%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%29%20OR+fulltext%3A%28%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%29%20OR+all_dc.description%3A%28%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%29%20%29%20%29&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=score&p_r_p_-1078056564_c=QF757YsWv58ICqkf4NaDXmZ4KnVD4FdH&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_o=1&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_order=desc&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_filter=dc.publicationdate_dt%3A%5B1970-01-01T00%3A00%3A00Z+TO+1979-12-31T15%3A59%3A59Z%5D|accessdate=2021-05-10|work=香港工商日報|date=1973-11-29|archive-date=2021-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512175249/https://mmis.hkpl.gov.hk/coverpage/-/coverpage/view?_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_hsf=%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_actual_q=(%20(%20allTermsMandatory:(true)%20OR+all_dc.title:(%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92)%20OR+all_dc.creator:(%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92)%20OR+all_dc.contributor:(%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92)%20OR+all_dc.subject:(%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92)%20OR+fulltext:(%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92)%20OR+all_dc.description:(%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BB%94%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92)%20)%20)&_coverpage_WAR_mmisportalportlet_sort_field=sc